OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLow cloud, hill and coastal
OL,6,Fmist and fog will be accompanied by
OL,7,Fpatchy drizzle at first. Skies will
OL,8,Fbrighten a little during the day
OL,9,Fthough, and feeling warm and quite
OL,10,Fhumid when the sun appears, with light
OL,11,Fwinds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud will thicken from the
OL,14,Fsouthwest this evening bringing
OL,15,Ffurther mist and fog patches along
OL,16,Fwith some outbreaks of rain. The rain
OL,17,Fwill turn more patchy overnight. Warm
OL,18,Fand humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
