OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FWednesday starts grey and
OL,6,Fmisty with patchy drizzle. Low cloud
OL,7,Fwill lift with some warm spells of
OL,8,Fsunshine developing during the day,
OL,9,Fthough still a chance of an afternoon
OL,10,Fshower.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FThursday will be rather cloudy and
OL,14,Fbreezy with patchy rain and fog,
OL,15,Fespecially in the north and west. Some
OL,16,Fwarm sunshine thereafter, though with
OL,17,Ffurther spells of rain too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
